      "text": "Oha Star Dance Dance Revolution (おはスタダンスダンスレボリューション, Oha Suta Dansu Dansu Reboryūshon) is a Dance Dance Revolution game for the Sony PlayStation console. The game features songs from the Japanese children's TV show Oha Star. There is no arcade counterpart.",
